window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Library is finally powering up, but missing books and faulty pillars threaten stability.</b></p> <p>In the aftermath of their last battle, several of Quinn's allies are still healing. In the meantime, while the Library and Lynx are still regaining all their memory pathways, Quinn must help resolve the mystery of the Ashiron pillar.</p> <p>But that's not their only problem. In order to expand the Library's power, more branches must be opened, but it's difficult to do that when not everyone is willing to return their books.</p> <p>Quinn must reactivate pillars, reopen more branches, hunt down the missing dimension books, and find the sabotage culprits. As long as she can master her own heritage before meeting any of her relatives, she might even have a chance.</p>"; 
